  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the trial is to study the efficacy of adding concomitant chemotherapy
      (carboplatin/5FU) to Erbitux-radiotherapy in patients with locally advanced head and neck
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
