  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Squamous cell carcinoma of oral cavity, oropharynx, hypopharynx, larynx

          -  Stage III - IV (T0-T4, N0-N2b, M0)

          -  Not resected

          -  Karnofsky PS&gt;=80

          -  Informed consent signed

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contra indication to chemotherapy or cetuximab
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
